steps: [1] If the team wins the semifinal, then the team qualifies for the final.
[2] If the team qualifies for the final, then the team plays for the championship.
[3] For every athlete, if the athlete passes the anti-doping test, then the athlete is eligible to compete.
[4] Athlete A passed the anti-doping test.
[6] The team qualified for the final.
[7] The team plays for the championship.
[8] Athlete A is eligible to compete.
[9] The team plays for the championship and Athlete A is eligible to compete.
